Management 


Intel Active Management Technology (AMT)
Remotely ask for disk and console IO to be redirected
Remotely update BIOS
This can be done over wireless or Ethernet
All packets can be read/blocked/mangled by AMT
Can read main memory
Turn off/Don't buy Intel Centrino Pro/Intel vPro

